1
00:00:01,075 --> 00:00:06,341
So if there are any deliberations by which you come to the control of our mind,

2
00:00:06,421 --> 00:00:09,840
whatever we do, is the mind’s doing.

3
00:00:12,280 --> 00:00:17,188
So if something is done like that, it is spontaneous according to them,

4
00:00:17,268 --> 00:00:20,708
