8
00:00:33,527 --> 00:00:36,460
Did you hear that Linda [Williams (Pearce)]?

9
00:00:36,540 --> 00:00:39,640
The question is very simple.

10
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:46,250
The question is this: that they were saying that the mind is limited. All right?

11
00:00:46,330 --> 00:00:51,537
Hello. Is Maria here? I was thinking of her. Where is she?

12
00:00:53,340 --> 00:00:54,540
I don’t see her.

13
00:00:57,610 --> 00:01:01,600
Hello! I was thinking of you today, somehow, to meet.

14
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:05,890
I’m very happy you could come.

15
00:01:05,970 --> 00:01:10,410
Now the question is this, a simple question,

16
00:01:10,490 --> 00:01:16,431
that they are saying that – through our mind whatever

17
00:01:16,511 --> 00:01:22,770
we do, and through the control of our mind whatever we do,

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:28,140
is done by a limited energy of mind. All right?

19
00:01:28,220 --> 00:01:31,030
Now this limited energy of mind,

20
00:01:31,110 --> 00:01:38,080
is doing something which cannot take you to unlimited.

21
00:01:40,250 --> 00:01:45,170
So something has to happen to us which is beyond the control of the mind.

22
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:49,240
That’s the only thing that is spontaneous.

23
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,921
Now see the confusion!

24
00:01:52,001 --> 00:01:57,628
Now on mental level you can answer that. Let’s see. Come along! Don. Who is there?

25
00:01:57,708 --> 00:02:02,788
Yogi: You could say it has to be something spontaneous that happens to you,

26
00:02:02,868 --> 00:02:04,934
