27
00:02:05,014 --> 00:02:09,280
Whereas these people were degrading themselves. Shri Mataji: No.

28
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:14,160
You see, but you see the proof of the awareness is not there, all right?

29
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,240
So they’ll say,

30
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:20,253
“How do you say you have a greater awareness?” because that is subjective.

31
00:02:20,333 --> 00:02:24,266
So they may come out you see. They are very clever. So now.

32
00:02:24,346 --> 00:02:25,759
Another answer here?

33
00:02:25,839 --> 00:02:27,972
Yogini: It’s another perception.

34
00:02:28,052 --> 00:02:29,918
Shri Mataji: The same thing!

35
00:02:29,998 --> 00:02:31,998
