37
00:02:36,691 --> 00:02:42,157
So you see on mental level, on discussion only, what can you say about Sahaj Yoga?

38
00:02:42,237 --> 00:02:44,717
Lets see. It’s a very good question.

39
00:02:44,797 --> 00:02:46,210
Put your mind to it.

40
00:02:46,290 --> 00:02:48,170
Very simple the answer is..

41
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:50,063
Yogi: Vibratory awareness.

42
00:02:50,143 --> 00:02:52,556
Shri Mataji: No, no, but that’s it:

43
00:02:52,636 --> 00:02:58,054
