44
00:02:58,134 --> 00:03:02,800
You may say anything but who will believe? “Come along, the computer!”

45
00:03:05,995 --> 00:03:07,195
It is very simple.

46
00:03:07,275 --> 00:03:12,341
You see, just go in a very simple way, then you will see the point. You may.

47
00:03:12,421 --> 00:03:16,404
Yogi: There’s, there’s no effort involved?

48
00:03:16,484 --> 00:03:19,164
