50
00:03:21,457 --> 00:03:24,457
Just on discussion point, what should we say?

51
00:03:24,537 --> 00:03:28,537
See that’s too far fetched [for them], “You see the results.

52
00:03:28,617 --> 00:03:30,350
I can feel your Kundalini.

53
