57
00:03:47,636 --> 00:03:50,169
Those want to cheat you will say that.

58
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,666
They can cheat you.

59
00:03:53,746 --> 00:03:58,279
If they want to cheat you, they’ll say, “Yes, we are using the mind!

60
00:03:58,359 --> 00:04:00,892
We are in perfect bliss and happiness.

61
00:04:00,972 --> 00:04:03,772
We have vibrations.” You know, if you say,

