00:04:03,852 --> 00:04:08,852
“Your Mooladhara is catching,” they’ll say, “Your this chakra is catching.”

63
00:04:08,932 --> 00:04:12,732
How can you quarrel with these people? –  On mental level

64
00:04:12,812 --> 00:04:17,425
, not on any substantial, what do you call the… proof’s to be given.

65
00:04:18,344 --> 00:04:24,517
Yogi: Mother, do they say the mind can see itself act, can be its own witness?

66
