74
00:04:53,034 --> 00:04:56,714
That’s too far fetched, Chaya. That’s too far fetched.

75
00:04:56,794 --> 00:05:00,260
They will not believe that your problems are solved.

76
00:05:00,340 --> 00:05:04,550
Only just on discussion point – what is the

77
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:09,849
