And she said, “What are you doing to me?” I know if I made it clear.

96
00:06:19,041 --> 00:06:22,454
You can hear, hear the lady, “What are you doing?”

97
00:06:22,534 --> 00:06:26,280
I was putting a bandhan on because my hand was shaking.

98
