105
00:06:52,842 --> 00:06:58,175
When you get to that position also you shout, howl – the same way you can do it.

106
00:06:58,272 --> 00:07:01,152
But you cannot make the Kundalini pulsate.

107
00:07:05,432 --> 00:07:10,578
Whatever you can do with your mind, and without your mind, is just the same,

108
00:07:10,658 --> 00:07:13,058
