124
00:08:18,674 --> 00:08:21,474
Divine does something which you cannot do.

125
00:08:21,554 --> 00:08:24,820
You cannot make cool breeze flow from your hands.

126
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:29,349
So if you go beyond mind it has

127
