129
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:41,177
Limited and unlimited are two different dimensions.

130
00:08:41,257 --> 00:08:44,390
This is the secret of your Mother’s maya, also.

131
00:08:44,470 --> 00:08:50,589
This is the secret of your Mother’s maya,

132
00:08:50,669 --> 00:08:54,402
