136
00:09:09,488 --> 00:09:15,021
Nobody can, shake, make you shake if you put the hand on the head, head of someone.

137
00:09:15,101 --> 00:09:18,120
So the Divine force is a thing which human

138
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:24,830
