you get out from there.

240
00:18:00,826 --> 00:18:03,892
You get out from there!” And when they say so,

241
00:18:03,972 --> 00:18:08,385
“You get out from there!” they say that, “We’ll put somebody else

242
00:18:08,465 --> 00:18:12,665
in your place and we’ll give you another place to go.” You see?

243
00:18:12,745 --> 00:18:18,345
Sort of a rapport is established; they are mediators, liaison officers, you can say.

244
00:18:18,425 --> 00:18:22,291
And they create this kind of an office by which they catch

245
00:18:22,371 --> 00:18:25,904
hold of these people and put them into somebody else.

246
00:18:25,984 --> 00:18:30,864
A very good example of this is a lady whose husband used to drink a lot,

247
00:18:30,944 --> 00:18:34,010
so she went to one of the ladies of this kind.

248
00:18:34,090 --> 00:18:38,507
So she said, “All right, I’ll manage this man and he won’t drink.

249
00:18:38,587 --> 00:18:41,187
So you have to give me a hundred rupees

250
00:18:41,267 --> 00:18:43,733
for that.” She paid a hundred rupees.

251
00:18:43,813 --> 00:18:47,064
So she put one bhoot in this man,

252
00:18:47,144 --> 00:18:52,210
removed this man who was drinking – you see there must be a drunkard in him.

253
00:18:52,290 --> 00:18:57,830
So this fellow started, you see he gave up drinking but he started going to races.

254
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:07,293
So she removed that bhoot and she put another one who started going to dirty women!

255
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:12,613
And then this lady got frightened, she said, “What are you doing?

256
00:19:12,693 --> 00:19:17,426
Every time I’m paying you hundred rupees, and hundred rupees,” you see?

257
00:19:17,506 --> 00:19:21,106
She had paid her a lot of money and suddenly she found

258
00:19:21,186 --> 00:19:25,150
that this fellow is doing all the three things together.

259
00:19:25,230 --> 00:19:28,437
So she went to fight with this woman! She said,

260
00:19:28,517 --> 00:19:33,783
“How dare you do these things to my husband!” And this lady put a bhoot in her.

261
00:19:33,863 --> 00:19:37,521
Since then that woman is still mad and

262
00:19:37,601 --> 00:19:39,881
I have not been able to cure her.

263
00:19:39,961 --> 00:19:45,494
So you can imagine how dangerous it is to go to these people for getting something!

264
00:19:45,574 --> 00:19:50,174
Still when she sees me she goes on like this and [she’s] quite funny.

265
00:19:50,254 --> 00:19:54,987
You remember one lady who came to [me]? The same one! This is the case.

266
00:19:55,067 --> 00:20:00,533
She’s a very good looking woman, married to a very rich man who owns a factory and

267
00:20:00,613 --> 00:20:05,879
this is the life both of them are leading, burning the candle on both the ends!

268
00:20:05,959 --> 00:20:07,359
So this is one thing.

269
00:20:07,439 --> 00:20:09,372
This is the one of the cases.

270
00:20:09,452 --> 00:20:12,652
The second case is of the supraconscious fellow.

271
00:20:12,732 --> 00:20:18,265
Now you go to a supraconscious fellow, like this doctor – who was that late doctor?

272
00:20:18,345 --> 00:20:23,891
Shri Mataji: … “Late Dr. Lamb’s Curative Centre,” you see. “International Curative

273
00:20:23,971 --> 00:20:28,184
[Centre]”. International bhoots he had! (laughter) Yes really!

274
00:20:28,264 --> 00:20:31,810
Curative Centre! And you had to write to them, that,

275
00:20:31,890 --> 00:20:36,023
“I am suffering from this disease.” Whatever disease you have.

276
00:20:36,103 --> 00:20:39,169
One lady was suffering from an uterus trouble.

277
00:20:39,249 --> 00:20:43,391
So all the great doctors you see, all the great lawyers,

278
00:20:43,471 --> 00:20:48,977
all the great scientists and all the great engineers and architects and all

279
00:20:49,057 --> 00:20:52,390
these great supraconscious people, very ambitious,

280
00:20:52,470 --> 00:20:58,024
Hitler and all such great warriors; all such people gather on the right hand side.

281
00:20:58,104 --> 00:21:01,570
So, he being a doctor, he met all his friends there.

282
00:21:01,650 --> 00:21:08,624
He met his friends and then by that, what happened that he could talk to them,

283
00:21:08,704 --> 00:21:12,970
“Now let’s start a clinic,” because these doctors would not die.

284
00:21:13,050 --> 00:21:17,450
They had been experimenting with this and experimenting with that.

285
00:21:17,530 --> 00:21:20,220
So they started this ‘Late Dr.

286
00:21:20,300 --> 00:21:22,990
Lamb’s clinic’ and for that,

287
00:21:23,070 --> 00:21:30,645
I don’t know if you know the whole story but if you

288
00:21:30,725 --> 00:21:34,791
read Gregoire’s book it might be there I think, that this Dr.

289
00:21:34,871 --> 00:21:38,180
Lamb lived in London who died and who had a son.

290
00:21:38,260 --> 00:21:42,215
Now this Dr. Lamb when he died his bhoot attacked a man in

291
00:21:42,295 --> 00:21:46,095
Vietnam where he was fighting and an ordinary soldier who

292
00:21:46,175 --> 00:21:51,788
had never known what is education is, you see, and he told him that “I am Dr. Lamb,

293
00:21:51,868 --> 00:21:57,334
I’m from such and such place. You’d better go to my son and tell him that you want

294
00:21:57,414 --> 00:22:00,547
to start this thing.” He did not attack his son

295
00:22:00,627 --> 00:22:04,160
because he knew his son wouldn’t be able to bear him,

296
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:07,320
because he wanted a very healthy, sturdy man, you see?

297
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:10,585
And this gentleman then went to this son and told him that,

298
00:22:10,665 --> 00:22:13,851
“Your father is within me and he’s talking like this.” He said,

299
00:22:13,931 --> 00:22:15,509
“I can’t believe it.” He said,

300
00:22:15,589 --> 00:22:18,641
“All right.” Then he went into trance, he started talking.

301
00:22:18,721 --> 00:22:23,476
He said, “See, we have got this things in the secret pocket, you go and see there’s

302
00:22:23,556 --> 00:22:27,822
money kept for you.” and, “We talked like this secretly and this

303
00:22:27,902 --> 00:22:31,368
was this…” And then the son had to believe, you see.

304
00:22:31,448 --> 00:22:32,848
Then he believed him.

305
00:22:32,928 --> 00:22:35,261
And he started this clinic for him.

306
00:22:35,341 --> 00:22:40,674
So he gave all the money and everything for the clinic and all the bhoot doctors

307
00:22:40,754 --> 00:22:46,220
– international – were helping this particular doctor to act anywhere they wanted.

308
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:49,671
So the intercommunication was established on that level,

309
00:22:49,751 --> 00:22:51,765
on the collective supraconscious.

310
00:22:51,845 --> 00:22:55,191
Now a lady was suffering from high blood pressure

311
00:22:55,271 --> 00:22:57,920
and kidney and also some uterus trouble.

312
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:01,310
So she went to them and she said that, “All right,

313
00:23:01,390 --> 00:23:03,906
I am suffering from such and such disease.”

314
00:23:03,986 --> 00:23:05,586
So they said “All right,

315
00:23:05,666 --> 00:23:10,266
you write a letter to our centre in London.” She wrote a letter here.

316
00:23:10,346 --> 00:23:13,946
So they sent back a letter that “On such and such date

317
00:23:14,026 --> 00:23:17,559
exactly…” You see living forces do not act like that,

318
00:23:17,639 --> 00:23:19,779
they don’t give you a date or thing.

319
00:23:19,859 --> 00:23:24,214
“On such and such date at this time we’ll appear within you and cure you.

320
00:23:24,294 --> 00:23:27,827
At that time, you lie down in your bed.” And suddenly

321
00:23:27,907 --> 00:23:31,040
she got this “O-ho-ho-ho-ho!” into her you see.

322
00:23:31,120 --> 00:23:34,466
So one of the doctors must have entered into her.

323
00:23:34,546 --> 00:23:37,506
And she got cured of it, absolutely cured.

324
00:23:37,586 --> 00:23:40,010
For a year or so she was all right.

325
00:23:40,090 --> 00:23:42,555
Then she started feeling very dizzy.

326
00:23:42,635 --> 00:23:46,996
She just started feeling very dizzy and all sorts of coming up.

327
00:23:47,076 --> 00:23:50,656
When she came to me she was in a tattered condition,

328
00:23:50,736 --> 00:23:54,082
absolutely finished; she was like this, you know.

329
00:23:54,162 --> 00:23:57,028
So, she knew that a spirit had come in her.

330
00:23:57,108 --> 00:24:02,654
But now she said, “There are at least ten or eleven of them within me, and I can’t

331
00:24:02,734 --> 00:24:08,267
bear them.” This kind of curing also can take place from the supraconscious people.

332
00:24:08,347 --> 00:24:13,080
Supposing there’s an architect, if he goes to one of such people he can

333
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:18,240
get an architect who is dead upon himself and he can start doing this work.

334
00:24:18,320 --> 00:24:23,200
Now this man who was a ripper and all that was himself, was possessed by

335
00:24:23,280 --> 00:24:28,280
some ripper who died or something like that, whose ambitions he is sharing.

336
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:32,093
You see you have to have inclination for that, no doubt.

337
00:24:32,173 --> 00:24:34,639
You have to have that weakness within

338
00:24:34,719 --> 00:24:36,852
you otherwise it won’t work out.

339
00:24:36,932 --> 00:24:38,865
But if you have that weakness

340
00:24:38,945 --> 00:24:40,611
and if you are very weak,

341
00:24:40,691 --> 00:24:44,984
otherwise also from mind, then these things catch hold of you.

342
00:24:45,064 --> 00:24:50,464
And if it has something to do with physical side the supraconscious can help you.

343
00:24:50,544 --> 00:24:53,557
If it has to do something on the mental side

344
00:24:53,637 --> 00:24:56,583
then the subconscious people can enter you.

345
00:24:56,663 --> 00:24:59,863
But they help you very temporarily and then they

346
00:24:59,943 --> 00:25:04,370
come back with a big force on you – it is like that.

347
00:25:04,450 --> 00:25:11,030
But Sahaj Yoga makes you so powerful and so pure that impurities just go out.

348
00:25:11,110 --> 00:25:13,910
It’s a cleansing force.

349
00:25:17,170 --> 00:25:23,041
It’s a very different thing where you neither put any bhoot into somebody,

350
00:25:23,121 --> 00:25:28,190
or your intention is not to cure but as a by-product people get cured.

351
00:25:30,781 --> 00:25:33,181
Now tremendous things are happening:

352
00:25:33,261 --> 00:25:39,070
like I met a lady and her husband in Australia – a

353
00:25:39,150 --> 00:25:42,155
very dynamic journalist – and the lady was

354
00:25:42,235 --> 00:25:46,381
the president of the Journalist Association. Do you know her?

355
00:25:46,461 --> 00:25:48,074
Shri Mataji: All right.

356
00:25:48,154 --> 00:25:50,554
Journalist Association of Australia.

357
00:25:50,634 --> 00:25:52,634
She could not have had a baby.

358
00:25:52,714 --> 00:25:55,580
Doctors had said she can never have a baby!

359
00:25:55,660 --> 00:26:02,876
She’ s very short, extremely fat; all that problem was there. Still they were

360
00:26:02,956 --> 00:26:07,550
carrying on. I mean, husband wanted the baby very much.

361
00:26:07,630 --> 00:26:11,760
And now she conceived, after Sahaj Yoga.

362
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:17,611
After so many years – fourteen, fifteen years of marriage now she’s conceived.

363
00:26:17,691 --> 00:26:20,851
So the her entire ideas about life are changed.

364
00:26:20,931 --> 00:26:24,931
She used to indulge into so many things that she used to do:

365
00:26:25,011 --> 00:26:27,521
she went to gurus, this, that, she did

366
00:26:27,601 --> 00:26:32,934
everything then she was a Catholic to begin with then she became something else,

367
00:26:33,014 --> 00:26:34,599
everything she has done.

368
00:26:34,679 --> 00:26:40,079
She overcame all that when she came to Sahaj Yoga and here she finds this answer,

369
00:26:40,190 --> 00:26:41,390
physically.

370
00:26:42,810 --> 00:26:45,076
So, I’ve not put any bhoot in her.

371
00:26:45,156 --> 00:26:48,556
I have made all the bhoots get out of her, you see.

372
00:26:48,636 --> 00:26:54,908
And she said that, “Now we are going to take up a project,” which I had told them,

373
00:26:54,988 --> 00:26:57,521
that “You have to expose these gurus.”

374
00:26:57,601 --> 00:27:01,001
Just even if you write what these people are doing,

375
00:27:01,081 --> 00:27:05,694
you will be able to show that this is madness, this is real madness!

376
00:27:06,522 --> 00:27:09,855
And once you have talked about it then you prepare

377
00:27:09,935 --> 00:27:13,401
a base for Sahaj Yoga and then you should say, “This

378
00:27:13,481 --> 00:27:17,540
is the reality that makes you sane,

379
00:27:17,620 --> 00:27:25,518
powerful and loving.” Then only

380
00:27:25,598 --> 00:27:29,300
people are going

381
00:27:29,380 --> 00:27:33,477
to see to this.

382
00:27:33,557 --> 00:27:37,690
So this is a very good thing that Sahaj Yoga creates miracles,

383
00:27:37,770 --> 00:27:39,370
really creates miracles.

384
00:27:40,610 --> 00:27:44,750
You have seen on material level, on mental level,

385
00:27:44,830 --> 00:27:49,060
on emotional level and ultimately on the spiritual level.

386
00:27:49,140 --> 00:27:52,840
You are all endowed with such powers.

387
00:27:53,564 --> 00:27:56,830
Even if you are doing anything wrong or anything,

388
00:27:56,910 --> 00:28:02,602
you are a realised-soul; if you want to give Realisation you can do it.

389
00:28:02,682 --> 00:28:05,969
For example, if this lamp is enlightened,

390
00:28:06,084 --> 00:28:08,950
it may not be good, it might be unclean, it

391
00:28:09,030 --> 00:28:11,816
may not be very good to burn,

392
00:28:11,896 --> 00:28:17,200
but once it is burning it can enlighten other lights.

393
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:19,820
Like that, your Spirit is pure.

394
00:28:22,510 --> 00:28:29,981
But one has to know that we have to fight all these evil spirits.

395
00:28:30,061 --> 00:28:35,154
On the unlimited I am working hard, very hard; that’s how they’re exposed.

396
00:28:35,234 --> 00:28:38,700
But on the limited you must work hard to fight them,

397
00:28:39,454 --> 00:28:41,920
and should be prepared to fight them.

398
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:44,800
You should prepare yourself to fight them;

399
00:28:44,880 --> 00:28:47,280
you have to fight these evil forces.

400
00:28:47,360 --> 00:28:50,090
Because they are the ones who are ruining

401
00:28:50,170 --> 00:28:55,592
your own beings around so you have to fight. There is big depression

402
00:28:55,672 --> 00:28:58,605
coming on you; people will just obstruct it,

403
00:28:58,685 --> 00:29:00,951
they’ll trouble you like anything.

404
00:29:01,031 --> 00:29:06,130
But you have to fight these and for that you should be strong.

405
00:29:06,210 --> 00:29:08,340
They are so strange.

406
00:29:08,420 --> 00:29:12,660
And the great people, the children of God,

407
00:29:12,740 --> 00:29:17,740
the men of God are born more in the West than in the East, most surprising.

408
00:29:17,820 --> 00:29:23,295
I think they were rewarded by God to come to a country which has more affluence,

409
00:29:23,375 --> 00:29:26,441
did not have so much poverty and the troubles.

410
00:29:26,521 --> 00:29:29,755
And these are the people who are lost,

411
00:29:29,835 --> 00:29:33,301
and the reason, one of them, which I discovered only

412
00:29:33,381 --> 00:29:37,171
yesterday, is that the modern concept of life is

413
00:29:37,251 --> 00:29:40,770
to make something that can be demolished easily.

414
00:29:40,850 --> 00:29:48,420
And this is what one should know that our foundations

415
00:29:48,500 --> 00:29:52,832
have been made very weak by satanic forces.

416
00:29:52,912 --> 00:29:54,912
Our foundations are very weak.

417
00:29:54,992 --> 00:30:00,192
We have been given all these ideas for days in and day out, the satanic forces

418
00:30:00,272 --> 00:30:05,085
have built it up since long; since long these ideas have been built up.

419
00:30:05,165 --> 00:30:09,165
On all the Western front if you see the kings how they were,

420
00:30:09,245 --> 00:30:12,845
the queens how they were, the way the people lived and

421
00:30:12,925 --> 00:30:17,725
the kind of life they led, and if you read the French this thing…I mean,

422
00:30:17,805 --> 00:30:20,405
sometimes you read other Kings of Spain

423
00:30:20,485 --> 00:30:24,351
and Portugal, you’re amazed, and the kind of life they led

424
00:30:24,431 --> 00:30:28,244
was so horrifyingly funny, even you can see the Catholic

425
00:30:28,324 --> 00:30:31,470
churches, the so called very religious people,

426
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:35,816
the way the pope lived, and all that is so horrifying sometimes!

427
00:30:35,896 --> 00:30:39,429
He even doesn’t know what is right and what is wrong!

428
00:30:39,509 --> 00:30:44,189
So your foundations were laid like that, wrongly, they are shaken up.

429
00:30:44,859 --> 00:30:47,325
You have to rebuild your foundations.

430
00:30:47,924 --> 00:30:52,790
So the foundations on which you stand, you [must] change them completely.

431
00:30:52,870 --> 00:30:56,707
You have new foundations of dharmic life.

432
00:30:56,787 --> 00:31:00,520
Absolutely you have to accept dharmic life in your life,

433
00:31:00,600 --> 00:31:04,094
that’s the way only your foundations can be good.

434
00:31:04,174 --> 00:31:08,240
In India the foundations are good – specially in Maharashtra,

435
00:31:08,320 --> 00:31:14,821
very good foundations they are – but the yearning,

436
00:31:14,901 --> 00:31:16,701
the aspiring, is not there.

437
00:31:16,781 --> 00:31:20,407
Like an aeroplane, one aeroplane which is got nicely

438
00:31:20,487 --> 00:31:24,087
built but it is so nicely built that it can never fly.

439
00:31:24,167 --> 00:31:26,500
The another one is so built that it

440
00:31:26,580 --> 00:31:28,980
wants to fly – as soon as takes off,

441
00:31:29,060 --> 00:31:33,865
everything goes and finished! (laughter) So,

442
00:31:33,945 --> 00:31:36,745
one must realise that our foundations were

443
00:31:36,825 --> 00:31:39,638
laid down like that by the satanic force.

444
00:31:39,718 --> 00:31:42,598
It’s much deeper than what you understand.

445
00:31:42,678 --> 00:31:47,811
You have to fight those foundations they’ll say, “Oh, what? He was like this,

446
00:31:47,891 --> 00:31:52,557
he was like that. Oh what?” They are not your ideals, one should know.

447
00:31:52,637 --> 00:31:58,037
They are not your ideals – these horrible kings who killed seven wives and things

448
00:31:58,117 --> 00:32:01,250
and things like that. They are not your ideals.

449
00:32:01,330 --> 00:32:03,478
Your ideals are your Self.

450
00:32:03,558 --> 00:32:07,449
You have to build new ideals in the Western countries.

451
00:32:07,529 --> 00:32:09,395
Then only you can change it.

452
00:32:09,475 --> 00:32:11,915
Because you are such a dynamic force.

453
00:32:11,995 --> 00:32:15,661
Every one of you have to come up to build yourself into

454
00:32:15,741 --> 00:32:21,450
ideals and try to lead a life of that ideal within you.

455
00:32:21,530 --> 00:32:25,705
You have to sacrifice, the greatest thing that you have to

456
00:32:25,785 --> 00:32:30,760
sacrifice is your ego which makes you so obstinate and hard-hearted.

457
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:35,845
Face yourself up! This ideal has to be created.

458
00:32:35,925 --> 00:32:38,725
There is someone sitting before you if you

459
00:32:38,805 --> 00:32:41,471
want to accept which is a very difficult

460
00:32:41,551 --> 00:32:48,160
life this side; that, one has to have compassion,

461
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:51,570
one has to have love, understanding.

462
00:32:51,650 --> 00:32:55,050
Never talk ill about each other, never.

463
00:32:55,560 --> 00:32:57,093
Try to help each other.

464
00:32:57,557 --> 00:33:01,490
We are very few. We cannot afford to fight among ourselves.

465
00:33:01,570 --> 00:33:05,400
We are very few people and wedded to a very great cause.

466
00:33:06,940 --> 00:33:08,901
So we cannot afford to fight.

467
00:33:08,981 --> 00:33:10,781
We cannot have wrong ideas.

468
00:33:10,861 --> 00:33:15,280
We cannot waste our time on mundane things, even like marriage.

469
00:33:17,620 --> 00:33:21,341
If marriage has to be, it has to be compatible, good,

470
00:33:21,421 --> 00:33:26,000
try to build up your things now; must try to patch up things.

471
00:33:26,527 --> 00:33:29,060
You have to make it a beautiful thing.

472
00:33:29,140 --> 00:33:33,400
Do not indulge onto small, nonsensical things which are petty,

473
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:36,650
useless otherwise we cannot do it.

474
00:33:36,730 --> 00:33:43,991
You see we have to still go a long way, a very long way we have to go.

475
00:33:44,071 --> 00:33:45,537
It’s a long, long way.

476
00:33:54,010 --> 00:33:57,640
These satanic forces are very

477
00:33:57,720 --> 00:34:02,201
nicely built up in these areas.

478
00:34:02,281 --> 00:34:06,840
They didn’t bother about India because India is a poor country.

479
00:34:08,020 --> 00:34:11,960
Poverty teaches one thing is to have proper foundations.

480
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:17,321
That’s the blessing of poverty: that once you give up even these

481
00:34:17,401 --> 00:34:22,401
foundations then nothing is with us, at least try to have some foundations.

482
00:34:23,370 --> 00:34:27,215
But the very poor are just the same as the very rich.

483
00:34:27,295 --> 00:34:32,361
But the very rich are not your ideals, not at all; [also] not the very poor.

484
00:34:32,441 --> 00:34:34,681
But you are your own ideals.

485
00:34:34,761 --> 00:34:36,940
You have to create new ideals.

486
00:34:37,020 --> 00:34:43,480
You are the new presidents of America and prime ministers of England.

487
00:34:43,560 --> 00:34:49,315
You are the one who are great people

488
00:34:49,395 --> 00:34:52,861
and you have to stand up to it: people of character,

489
00:34:52,941 --> 00:34:58,230
of integrity, of hard work, proper understanding,

490
00:34:58,310 --> 00:35:01,711
otherwise you cannot do anything.

491
00:35:01,791 --> 00:35:03,124
You have to come up!

492
00:35:03,685 --> 00:35:08,351
It’s easy to study something, pass M.A., or MHD or anything like that,

493
00:35:08,431 --> 00:35:12,810
but to become an ideal you have to mature.

494
00:35:12,890 --> 00:35:20,600
You have to tell yourself that, “I have to come up, I have to do this!”

495
00:35:20,680 --> 00:35:26,430
Which is not difficult now because you have the source under your command!

496
00:35:28,530 --> 00:35:30,031
Anything is possible.

497
00:35:30,111 --> 00:35:34,387
Just ask for it and you’ll have it. But build it up.

498
00:35:34,467 --> 00:35:37,290
Even now if you cannot build up your own

499
00:35:37,370 --> 00:35:42,835
personality and the new ideals when will you do? When I am here with all

500
00:35:42,915 --> 00:35:44,181
the chakras intact.

501
00:35:44,261 --> 00:35:51,570
Easy to justify yourself.

502
00:35:51,650 --> 00:35:57,798
There’s no justification needed for anything.

503
00:35:57,878 --> 00:36:04,299
“This is wrong, that is wrong.” – all finished!

504
00:36:04,379 --> 00:36:07,303
You have to become that.

505
00:36:07,383 --> 00:36:10,316
So one is, that you change your foundations.

506
00:36:11,318 --> 00:36:14,784
Despite all this, we have people like William Blake,

507
00:36:14,864 --> 00:36:17,330
Shakespeare, Tennyson – great people.

508
00:36:17,410 --> 00:36:20,231
Tremendous people, Mozart, this, that.

509
00:36:20,311 --> 00:36:25,030
Lots of people in this country also.

510
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:28,387
Taking their names itself liberates vibrations.

511
00:36:28,467 --> 00:36:33,069
In those conditions, single-handed, they created their own ideals.

512
00:36:33,149 --> 00:36:37,472
Just think of them how they must have fought this horrible… it

513
00:36:37,552 --> 00:36:42,094
is only today that we accept him, who accepts these people? Jung?

514
00:36:42,174 --> 00:36:47,010
Who accepts him? Only twelve Jungians – horrible Jungians these are.

515
00:36:47,090 --> 00:36:49,890
Every one of you is capable of doing that.

516
00:36:53,704 --> 00:36:56,370
Every one of you has to become a leader.

517
00:36:56,450 --> 00:37:01,534
In Poland an ordinary factory worker did that (Lech Wałęsa).

518
00:37:01,614 --> 00:37:03,880
He was an ordinary factory worker.

519
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:06,140
But he was not a realised-soul.

520
00:37:06,220 --> 00:37:11,086
He could not communicate with God, he had no way of knowing the Absolute.

521
00:37:15,370 --> 00:37:20,170
So channelise yourself properly, cleanse yourself properly and dedicate.

522
00:37:22,640 --> 00:37:25,640
For dedication you don’t have to do anything.

523
00:37:25,730 --> 00:37:29,310
I do not want anything from you for dedication,

524
00:37:29,390 --> 00:37:34,316
except give up your egos and superegos, that’s all.

525
00:37:34,396 --> 00:37:37,583
These loads you must take it out.

526
00:37:37,663 --> 00:37:43,651
Just create a little space there, which is the heart actually.

527
00:37:43,731 --> 00:37:49,011
A little space and it will work out. And that is, one has to understand now,

528
00:37:49,091 --> 00:37:54,460
when you these films and things – thank God I did not see.

529
00:37:54,540 --> 00:37:57,340
You see it’s easy to kill these rakshasas,

530
00:37:57,420 --> 00:38:03,963
it’s easy do all this but what about these lost souls?

531
00:38:04,043 --> 00:38:08,643
Everything works out very well, say about a year or so, or two years.

532
00:38:08,723 --> 00:38:11,203
After that I am going to blast them.

533
00:38:11,283 --> 00:38:13,416
Before that you should be ready.

534
00:38:13,496 --> 00:38:17,362
Because once I blast them they’ll come back on you people.

535
00:38:17,442 --> 00:38:22,108
So you should be such strong people that you are not finished by that.

536
00:38:22,188 --> 00:38:24,654
You see blasting is so easy for them.

537
00:38:24,734 --> 00:38:28,800
For me it’s the easiest thing to blast all of them and finish

538
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:33,341
them off but once they go to subconscious area they’ll attack

539
00:38:33,421 --> 00:38:38,740
you again so I want them to live, with paralysis, with diabetes,

540
00:38:38,820 --> 00:38:42,753
with all sort of things; but they’ll live, they’ll not die.

541
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:49,360
It’s a tremendous task and I’m working twenty-four hours [a day], twenty-four hours.

542
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:54,220
I have no sleep, nothing, you know that.

543
00:38:54,300 --> 00:38:57,725
It’s all just a life that

544
00:38:57,805 --> 00:39:04,250
is so enjoying and itself.

545
00:39:05,890 --> 00:39:11,624
The whole vision I can see clearly of those beautiful days when we all will

546
00:39:11,704 --> 00:39:16,650
be enjoying each other and the bliss of God together – that’s all I want.

547
00:39:17,990 --> 00:39:23,270
We have to pull out so many human beings from the clutches of the evil forces,

548
00:39:23,350 --> 00:39:25,416
for which you have to dedicate.

549
00:39:26,539 --> 00:39:29,552
Our attention is too much on useless things,

550
00:39:29,632 --> 00:39:33,365
materialistic things: there’s no end to it. Be satisfied

551
00:39:33,445 --> 00:39:35,725
with less. There is no end to it.

552
00:39:35,805 --> 00:39:40,471
You will be looked after also materially; there won’t be much problem.

553
00:39:40,551 --> 00:39:43,551
But don’t run after too many of these things.

554
00:39:43,631 --> 00:39:45,897
Just don’t have interest in these.

555
00:39:45,977 --> 00:39:48,123
What is it all? It’s all trash!

556
00:39:48,203 --> 00:39:51,003
But you should be loving and affectionate.

557
00:39:51,083 --> 00:39:57,606
You see, once you start giving up these things, what you become [is] you become

558
00:39:57,686 --> 00:40:03,809
like a hard-hearted person: “I have no interest in anything!” – finished.

559
00:40:03,889 --> 00:40:06,464
Who has interest in such a stone?

560
00:40:06,544 --> 00:40:09,024
(Shri Mataji talks to a child) Good.

561
00:40:09,104 --> 00:40:12,784
You are feeling cool breeze in the hand? She’s just in

562
00:40:12,864 --> 00:40:16,610
meditation. Yogi: She says her hands feel nice, Mother.

563
00:40:16,690 --> 00:40:21,690
Shri Mataji: She’s in meditation actually. Yogi: Sometimes at home. Mother,

564
00:40:21,770 --> 00:40:27,036
she sits in front of Your photograph and she won’t speak to anybody afterwards.

565
00:40:27,116 --> 00:40:31,494
She just, she’ll just wander around and she’ll play with her toys,

566
00:40:31,574 --> 00:40:34,240
but she doesn’t want to speak to people.

567
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,986
She just goes very quiet.

568
00:40:36,066 --> 00:40:38,060
Shri Mataji: Let them grow up.

569
00:40:38,140 --> 00:40:40,040
But you are the foundations.

570
00:40:41,920 --> 00:40:44,933
Now they will talk of you as the foundation,

571
00:40:45,013 --> 00:40:47,879
not of these horrible people who have been.

572
00:40:47,959 --> 00:40:52,752
They will talk of you, “Oh, such and such person was the Sahaj Yogi,

573
00:40:52,832 --> 00:40:56,432
the first Sahaj Yogis.” Where is that, the first one?

574
00:41:00,436 --> 00:41:02,902
He’s not there, missing all the time.

575
00:41:02,982 --> 00:41:06,220
Yogi: He’s getting the door!

576
00:41:06,300 --> 00:41:10,213
Shri Mataji: Will you come in?

577
00:41:10,293 --> 00:41:14,275
(laughter) Come here in front! That is how they

578
00:41:14,355 --> 00:41:18,421
have to talk. You have to be ideals of love and affection and

579
00:41:18,501 --> 00:41:22,659
not of domination and nonsense – all of you.

580
00:41:25,119 --> 00:41:27,585
You will be the first Sahaj Yogis.

581
00:41:27,665 --> 00:41:32,345
You are the one who are going to change the complete concept of life.

582
00:41:33,105 --> 00:41:35,638
The new ideals have to be established.

583
00:41:44,705 --> 00:41:49,305
I don’t know if you people really are aware of your responsibilities.

584
00:41:50,948 --> 00:41:56,148
Sometimes you are only worried on, “Oh! Where am I catching? What is happening

585
00:41:56,228 --> 00:41:58,841
to me? What is this?” So self-centred!

586
00:41:58,921 --> 00:42:03,054
Or you are worried about others: “She should not have not done

587
00:42:03,134 --> 00:42:07,534
this!” “He should not done, he should have not sat next to Mother!

588
00:42:07,614 --> 00:42:10,680
He should have done this.” Nobody should think

589
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:13,493
that they love me more than anybody else.

590
00:42:13,573 --> 00:42:15,573
Nobody should think like that!

591
00:42:15,653 --> 00:42:19,519
Some people know more rituals, some know more in protocol,

592
00:42:19,599 --> 00:42:22,265
doesn’t matter; but I know who loves me.

593
00:42:22,345 --> 00:42:25,211
The one who loves others loves me the most.

594
00:42:25,291 --> 00:42:29,557
I don’t care [about] your protocols and your ritualistic things.

595
00:42:29,637 --> 00:42:31,461
It’s nonsense for me. What does it

596
00:42:31,541 --> 00:42:36,354
matter for me? The one who loves others is the one who really loves me.

597
00:42:36,434 --> 00:42:37,580
Take it from me.

598
00:42:37,660 --> 00:42:42,078
I have had all these rituals and all that and I have no care for these things.

599
00:42:42,158 --> 00:42:45,421
Makes no difference whether you say, “Good morning,” to me or,

600
00:42:45,501 --> 00:42:48,314
“Good evening to me,” it’s not important.

601
00:42:48,394 --> 00:42:53,079
What you say to your brothers and sisters is the most important point.

602
00:42:53,159 --> 00:42:57,554
Sahaja Yoga will never work out if you do not look after that side: how you behave

603
00:42:57,634 --> 00:42:59,739
towards your wife, towards your husband,

604
00:42:59,819 --> 00:43:01,608
towards your brothers and sisters.

605
00:43:01,688 --> 00:43:03,368
That is the most important thing.

606
00:43:03,448 --> 00:43:05,914
Anybody who tries to play such tricks

607
00:43:05,994 --> 00:43:07,794
will get out of Sahaj Yoga.

608
00:43:07,874 --> 00:43:13,007
You know that I’ve thrown out very, so-called ‘important’ people out of Sahaj

609
00:43:13,087 --> 00:43:15,020
Yoga when they did like this,

610
00:43:15,100 --> 00:43:18,366
to dominate others, by saying, “This is not good!

611
00:43:18,446 --> 00:43:22,779
You should not put your hand there!” or “Put your feet there!” or

612
00:43:22,859 --> 00:43:24,992
“Do this and that.” Who can know

613
00:43:25,072 --> 00:43:27,072
the protocol of Divine Mother?

614
00:43:27,152 --> 00:43:29,418
You cannot bind me into protocols.

615
00:43:29,498 --> 00:43:34,017
You can not bind me to anything I am unlimited. I am detached.

616
00:43:34,097 --> 00:43:36,243
You cannot bind me to anything.

617
00:43:36,323 --> 00:43:41,069
To think that you can have me attracted towards you by your protocols,

618
00:43:41,149 --> 00:43:43,149
which is dead, has no meaning.

619
00:43:43,229 --> 00:43:48,725
It has to be a living protocol of being kind and generous, being beautiful.

620
00:43:48,831 --> 00:43:53,497
Some are lethargic: Say a husband wants the wife to work all the time.

621
00:43:53,577 --> 00:43:56,310
The wife wants the husband to every time.

622
00:43:56,390 --> 00:43:59,123
Everybody finding faults with each other!

623
00:43:59,203 --> 00:44:00,936
They are not Sahaja Yogis.

624
00:44:01,016 --> 00:44:04,149
Sahaja Yogis are the people who take it sahaja.

625
00:44:05,717 --> 00:44:10,317
If somebody is not working that person will go down – just like this.

626
00:44:10,397 --> 00:44:13,743
I’ll put that person out of Sahaja Yoga. But why?

627
00:44:13,823 --> 00:44:17,089
Why did you come to Sahaja Yoga? You are seekers.

628
00:44:17,169 --> 00:44:20,835
You have been seeking for ages now. You have been built

629
00:44:20,915 --> 00:44:24,296
up from ages now. Are you going to waste your life?

630
00:44:24,376 --> 00:44:28,789
In any case you have to sleep and rest for the rest of your life.

631
00:44:28,869 --> 00:44:31,949
So why not now work it out. In every way act!

632
00:44:32,029 --> 00:44:35,375
Firstly you will become real, very good citizens,

633
00:44:35,455 --> 00:44:38,535
with moral values which are your foundations.

634
00:44:38,615 --> 00:44:41,665
You yourself judge you are realised-souls.

635
00:44:41,745 --> 00:44:43,691
I’ll leave it to your judge.

636
00:44:43,771 --> 00:44:46,917
I can not going to tell you why did you do it.

637
00:44:46,997 --> 00:44:49,343
No, it is you, you judge yourself.

638
00:44:49,423 --> 00:44:51,436
You will lose your vibration.

639
00:44:51,516 --> 00:44:53,462
And losing vibrations is the

640
00:44:53,542 --> 00:44:55,088
You can become silent.

641
00:44:55,168 --> 00:44:57,581
Silence can be from other agencies.

642
00:44:57,661 --> 00:45:02,074
Negative forces from the left side of the Agnya are giving ideas.

643
00:45:02,154 --> 00:45:07,554
You must have your own ideas. “I can’t, I go on thinking,” this nonsense goes on.

644
00:45:07,634 --> 00:45:12,380
Just tell yourself how dare you do all this nonsense of the Left Side.

645
00:45:12,460 --> 00:45:16,326
Those who are left sided better go in for lemon treatment,

646
00:45:16,406 --> 00:45:19,686
beating [with] shoes, everything. Get out of it!

647
00:45:19,766 --> 00:45:22,712
Those who are Right Sided better go on with

648
00:45:22,792 --> 00:45:28,274
a nice hundred and eight beating to oneself. Get in the centre! Cleanse yourself!

649
00:45:28,354 --> 00:45:32,562
If you really love yourself you cleanse yourself. Be in the centre.

650
00:45:32,642 --> 00:45:37,375
Never be proud of your ego, never be proud – “Oh, I think it’s correct.

651
00:45:37,455 --> 00:45:40,921
Yes I feel..” Beat yourself hundred and eight times.

652
00:45:41,018 --> 00:45:45,084
You see, you can be very high handed under the circumstances.

653
00:45:45,164 --> 00:45:49,830
You can do absolutely without any embarrassment of what you are doing,

654
00:45:49,910 --> 00:45:52,843
you can be absolutely shameless, you can be.

655
00:45:52,930 --> 00:45:56,089
I mean, you are a Sahaj Yogi! How can that be?

656
00:45:56,169 --> 00:46:01,169
You should feel embarrassed about things. There should be a little sankoch.

657
00:46:01,249 --> 00:46:07,300
You call it ‘formality’ but I would not it ‘formal’. ‘Sankoch’ is the thing:  “Ho

658
00:46:07,380 --> 00:46:13,210
w to do this?” “Why to hurt anyone?” There should be such reservations about you.

659
00:46:13,290 --> 00:46:18,778
How can you say such a thing to someone? It will hurt.

660
00:46:18,858 --> 00:46:21,804
One if the victims of this is David Baxter.

661
00:46:23,055 --> 00:46:26,855
He was hurt so much that his Agnya bloated more and more.

662
00:46:26,935 --> 00:46:30,801
Because if your Agnya is hurt, your Agnya just bloats out;

663
00:46:30,881 --> 00:46:33,147
you don’t know what to do with it.

664
00:46:35,347 --> 00:46:37,280
So many are like that I know.

665
00:46:37,360 --> 00:46:42,400
Somebody tries to show off they are big gurus and try to push down others:

666
00:46:42,480 --> 00:46:43,893
“Oh, I know, I know.

667
00:46:43,973 --> 00:46:47,653
I know Sahaj Yoga, I’m a great Sahaj Yoga this thing!”

668
00:46:47,733 --> 00:46:50,999
And then I will make a [horn] come out like that!

669
00:46:51,079 --> 00:46:56,808
A horn. But that comes out from here.

670
00:46:56,888 --> 00:47:02,221
You see in the mirror, you can see your ego jutting out from here. Just feel it.

671
00:47:02,301 --> 00:47:07,904
All of you. It’s there. Push it down.

672
00:47:07,984 --> 00:47:13,450
This nonsense, this is the sticking point, you know! Though the balloon goes thin,

673
00:47:13,530 --> 00:47:17,658
it’s sticking on here; there’s a sticker. Push it down.

674
00:47:17,738 --> 00:47:21,350
Here it bloats outs.

675
00:47:21,430 --> 00:47:25,125
This is how Buddha is…Buddha.

676
00:47:25,205 --> 00:47:30,605
Buddha is the one who is realised: ‘buddha,’ the one who is [an] enlightened one.

677
00:47:30,685 --> 00:47:34,535
You are the enlightened one, how can you have an ego?

678
00:47:34,615 --> 00:47:37,148
You are the buddha: the one who knows.

679
00:47:39,105 --> 00:47:41,971
You are buddha, you are enlightened people.

680
00:47:42,845 --> 00:47:44,445
Put your hand over here.

681
00:47:44,525 --> 00:47:47,791
Ego is the greatest enemy. I have seen people who

682
00:47:47,871 --> 00:47:52,071
suffer from superego: if you take it out they’ll go to the ego.

683
00:47:53,410 --> 00:47:58,831
It’s the greatest enemy you have, this superego, when there is no ego.

684
00:47:58,911 --> 00:48:02,321
But if there is ego then whatever you may

685
00:48:02,401 --> 00:48:05,267
try with superego it will come back to ego.

686
00:48:07,460 --> 00:48:11,910
So for us, in the West, we have the greatest problem – is of ego.

687
00:48:11,990 --> 00:48:14,590
Whatever appeals to ego we run to that.

688
00:48:14,670 --> 00:48:17,189
That’s how these people are made mad.

689
00:48:17,269 --> 00:48:21,082
They said, “Oh,  you can fly.” (in TM) – gone into that.

690
00:48:21,162 --> 00:48:25,656
Somebody will say that you’ll become very powerful — gone into it.

691
00:48:25,736 --> 00:48:29,753
Somebody said that you will become a great guru — finished!

692
00:48:29,833 --> 00:48:35,090
When you become the Spirit you become one with the Whole — nobody says that.

693
00:48:35,170 --> 00:48:40,000
That’s Jewish! (laughing).

694
00:48:45,120 --> 00:48:47,320
I am not saying yet too!

695
00:48:51,095 --> 00:48:54,161
But Australia definitely is doing much better.

696
00:48:54,241 --> 00:48:58,210
They have a little love.

697
00:48:58,290 --> 00:49:02,826
That day I don’t know why; just can’t say

698
00:49:02,906 --> 00:49:06,304
Now, it’s coming again. Better?

699
00:49:06,384 --> 00:49:12,330
When I say, “You are realised,” “You are great,” “You

700
00:49:12,410 --> 00:49:16,121
are saints,” [there’s] one more blow into the balloon!

701
00:49:19,675 --> 00:49:23,541
If I say, “You have  to create your ideals,” one more blow

702
00:49:23,621 --> 00:49:27,221
: is the balloon going on blowing up. When I say that,

703
00:49:27,301 --> 00:49:34,310
I say it to create that awareness within

704
00:49:34,390 --> 00:49:38,990
you that you are here for the torches.

705
00:49:39,090 --> 00:49:40,423
You are the torches.

706
00:49:44,390 --> 00:49:48,920
But the torches are to be ego-less!

707
00:49:51,475 --> 00:49:54,541
Because your ideals have been all full of ego.

708
00:49:54,621 --> 00:50:01,550
See anybody; say Churchill standing there with a stick in his hand — same thing.

709
00:50:01,630 --> 00:50:06,967
It’s nothing but complete body looks like an ego, like that. Anyone!

710
00:50:07,047 --> 00:50:11,028
These ideals have to go away. We have to form new ideals.

711
00:50:11,108 --> 00:50:13,018
He was all right for war.

712
00:50:13,098 --> 00:50:16,898
We needed him for war, to meet another ego called Hitler.

713
00:50:16,978 --> 00:50:20,311
So it was all right to break their heads together.

714
00:50:20,391 --> 00:50:22,511
But now we need new ideals.

715
00:50:22,591 --> 00:50:25,221
That time is over now.

716
00:50:25,301 --> 00:50:31,540
When there is flood you need boats to carry you across,

717
00:50:31,641 --> 00:50:36,441
but after reaching the shores you don’t carry the boats with you do you?

718
00:50:36,521 --> 00:50:40,516
You leave them behind. But we don’t.

719
00:50:41,980 --> 00:50:45,690
These boats are no good for us now we’ve done the job.

720
00:50:45,770 --> 00:50:50,740
Now we have to go ahead with our own feet.

721
00:50:50,820 --> 00:50:54,630
All right?

722
00:50:54,710 --> 00:50:58,350
So no bloating of the ego should be there.

723
00:51:01,070 --> 00:51:04,254
And with that one would realise that we should

724
00:51:04,334 --> 00:51:07,414
not think that in any way we are exceptional.

725
00:51:07,494 --> 00:51:10,494
No one should think that you are exceptional!

726
00:51:10,574 --> 00:51:14,804
If you start thinking that only you are blowing up your ego.

727
00:51:14,884 --> 00:51:16,430
To Mother you are not.

728
00:51:16,510 --> 00:51:18,910
You have to be ideal. You have to be

729
00:51:18,990 --> 00:51:23,820
in the centre. You have to be a Sahaj Yogi.

730
00:51:23,900 --> 00:51:26,233
That’s the most important thing is.

731
00:51:28,070 --> 00:51:32,464
Do not judge yourself by what you think of yourself,

732
00:51:32,544 --> 00:51:37,810
but what your Mother thinks of you. How much joy you are giving to your Mother?

733
00:51:37,890 --> 00:51:45,821
If you make her unhappy

734
00:51:45,901 --> 00:51:53,220
then what’s the use.

735
00:51:53,300 --> 00:52:00,664
Now don’t go into [Left Vishuddhi].  (laughter) What a game eh? Immediately!

736
00:52:00,744 --> 00:52:02,210
There’s a pocket here.

737
00:52:02,290 --> 00:52:05,490
The whole balloon goes down there, settles down.

738
00:52:05,570 --> 00:52:08,170
Again as soon as I say something, “Oh!”

739
00:52:08,250 --> 00:52:13,285
Now you must have noticed that there are

740
00:52:13,365 --> 00:52:20,881
very few really seekers

741
00:52:20,961 --> 00:52:23,698
in this world, who are true seekers.

742
00:52:23,778 --> 00:52:27,511
And those who are seekers must realise also that seekers

743
00:52:27,591 --> 00:52:31,057
cannot be happy with anything else but their Spirit.

744
00:52:32,040 --> 00:52:36,067
This is the test of a seeker.

745
00:52:36,147 --> 00:52:39,280
And a non-seeker can never understand a seeker.

746
00:52:39,360 --> 00:52:44,360
And it is very difficult to live with a man or a woman who is not a seeker.

747
00:52:44,440 --> 00:52:51,345
Because you catch all the bad points and you suffer. [If] the person has an ego,

748
00:52:51,425 --> 00:52:56,625
you feel the thing here, [but] the person doesn’t feel anything. He’s hurting?

749
00:52:57,105 --> 00:52:58,505
He’s very nicely off!

750
00:52:58,585 --> 00:53:02,118
He has his ego intact and he’s torturing you as well!

751
00:53:03,555 --> 00:53:06,768
But a person who is a seeker is a better person

752
00:53:06,848 --> 00:53:09,514
because you can give Realisation to that

753
00:53:09,594 --> 00:53:13,260
person and then your vibratory awareness can be shared,

754
00:53:13,340 --> 00:53:15,340
and nobody would mind anymore.

755
00:53:15,420 --> 00:53:20,486
But somebody who is not at all a seeker could be a very difficult situation.

756
00:53:25,110 --> 00:53:28,154
You cannot make a fruit into a flower.

757
00:53:29,994 --> 00:53:32,140
And the flower becomes a fruit.

758
00:53:32,220 --> 00:53:35,553
Now you are changed, so you have become the fruit.

759
00:53:35,633 --> 00:53:37,899
But you must have a flower around,

760
00:53:37,979 --> 00:53:43,215
if you have a flower you can make it into a fruit. But if it’s a leaf? No idea!

761
00:53:43,295 --> 00:53:48,708
Like “My mother, my brother, my father, my husband, my wife,” and this and that.

762
00:53:48,788 --> 00:53:52,121
Those who are already entangled with such problems

763
00:53:52,201 --> 00:53:54,934
should learn to not to get more problems.

764
00:53:57,769 --> 00:54:02,249
Those who are not flowers should be avoided, forgotten and locked.

765
00:54:02,329 --> 00:54:04,262
Don’t do anything about them.

766
00:54:04,342 --> 00:54:07,608
You just don’t worry. The more you try to improve

767
00:54:07,688 --> 00:54:12,354
them the worse you’ll become. They can never improve. I give you a big

768
00:54:12,434 --> 00:54:16,836
rope to see. If they are not seekers they will never be a seeker.

769
00:54:16,916 --> 00:54:19,448
You cannot inject seeking into them.

770
00:54:19,528 --> 00:54:23,328
They may come [for] some material well-being, this, that,

771
00:54:23,408 --> 00:54:26,874
but they can never become seekers and you forget it!

772
00:54:26,954 --> 00:54:29,554
You may have to suffer because of them.

773
00:54:29,634 --> 00:54:32,900
Because if they are catching, you have to suffer.

774
00:54:33,004 --> 00:54:36,950
If they have a Nabhi Chakra, you have to suffer: no doubt.

775
00:54:37,030 --> 00:54:40,150
But you have committed a mistake and forget it.

776
00:54:40,230 --> 00:54:41,687
It can never improve.

777
00:54:41,767 --> 00:54:45,047
The person is very difficult to become a seeker.

778
00:54:45,127 --> 00:54:46,793
Do not waste your energy.

779
00:54:46,873 --> 00:54:51,219
Christ has said, “Don’t throw your pearls [before the swine].” ”

780
00:54:51,299 --> 00:54:55,165
You cannot force anybody to be a seeker; you cannot force.

781
00:54:55,245 --> 00:54:59,311
But there are millions and millions of seekers in this world.

782
00:54:59,391 --> 00:55:04,791
So forget about all such relationships and say that, “You are finished.” They may

783
00:55:04,871 --> 00:55:10,337
call you mad, they make all you crazy, they make all you anything, [but] they will

784
00:55:10,417 --> 00:55:15,963
realise only one thing that you lead a much better life than they do; you are much

785
00:55:16,043 --> 00:55:19,305
more peaceful, blissful and dharmic and sane,

786
00:55:19,385 --> 00:55:25,760
but they won’t accept your life. Forget it!

787
00:55:25,840 --> 00:55:30,173
Just play around with them understanding that they cannot change.

788
00:55:30,790 --> 00:55:35,111
Even if they change mentally they cannot have that urge to be

789
00:55:35,191 --> 00:55:39,724
seeking because for a seeker, nothing matters, nothing is important.

790
00:55:39,804 --> 00:55:45,890
Nothing gives them joy: even a little child like that. She’s gone off!

791
00:55:45,970 --> 00:55:47,310
They are so relaxed.

792
00:55:51,670 --> 00:55:54,530
So, any more questions? Mio?

793
00:55:54,610 --> 00:56:01,650
Cooly and Mio should come and see me tomorrow…

794
00:56:01,730 --> 00:56:07,313
Shri Mataji: ..before going to the program.

795
00:56:07,393 --> 00:56:09,964
Coming to the program. You come here,

796
00:56:10,044 --> 00:56:12,390
come there. I want to talk to you.

797
00:56:21,570 --> 00:56:24,450
Antoinette Wells: I have another question:

798
00:56:37,409 --> 00:56:40,209
What about the people who are good people,

799
00:56:40,289 --> 00:56:45,622
dharmic people, not seekers, who have got realisation but don’t see now the big…

800
00:56:45,702 --> 00:56:49,902
Shri Mataji: …vision. Lady: The vision what’s going on at the –

801
00:56:49,982 --> 00:56:52,848
Shri Mataji: They’ll go out of circulation.

802
00:56:52,928 --> 00:56:55,061
They have to come in Sahaj Yoga.

803
00:56:55,141 --> 00:56:57,741
They go out of circulation, absolutely.

804
00:56:57,821 --> 00:57:01,087
You see, the thing is, Sahaj Yoga doesn’t accept.

805
00:57:01,167 --> 00:57:03,100
It rejects more than accepts.

806
00:57:03,180 --> 00:57:04,913
It’s a judgement going on.

807
00:57:04,993 --> 00:57:09,259
Such people who go out of Realisation, they have to work it out.

808
00:57:09,339 --> 00:57:11,940
You may talk to them because they’re realised,

809
00:57:12,020 --> 00:57:14,735
you can give them bandhan, you can work on them.

810
00:57:14,815 --> 00:57:19,396
They are the people in whom you could be interested, but they are lost otherwise.

811
00:57:19,476 --> 00:57:22,360
I had given a very good example of this [which] was

812
00:57:22,440 --> 00:57:26,479
that they make butter out of the…what you call that? We call it ‘curd’.

813
00:57:26,559 --> 00:57:28,165
It’s yoghurt. They churn it.

814
00:57:28,245 --> 00:57:31,525
When they churn it what happens [is] some butter comes up,

815
00:57:31,605 --> 00:57:34,456
the rest remains as buttermilk. How do they do it?

816
00:57:34,536 --> 00:57:39,310
To separate it from that, they put a big lump of butter in that. Then they churn it.

817
00:57:39,390 --> 00:57:43,745
Now the whole butter gets round that big lump and it gathers into a big lump.

818
00:57:43,825 --> 00:57:46,709
But there are some particles which are left behind;

819
00:57:46,789 --> 00:57:49,108
they are butter, they are not buttermilk.

820
00:57:49,188 --> 00:57:54,588
If they do not stick to this big thing, they are thrown away with the buttermilk.

821
00:57:54,668 --> 00:57:59,206
So those who do not come up to Sahaj Yoga, who are not up to the mark,

822
00:57:59,286 --> 00:58:02,486
will be all thrown out, no doubt, that’s a fact.

823
00:58:02,566 --> 00:58:04,699
You have to come up to the mark.

824
00:58:04,779 --> 00:58:07,245
And you should not worry about those.

825
00:58:07,325 --> 00:58:09,258
You should have nirapekshita.

826
00:58:09,338 --> 00:58:13,604
You should have no attachment for such people. No channa for me?

827
00:58:13,684 --> 00:58:15,484
Can you give me some water?

828
00:58:15,564 --> 00:58:19,710
That’s good to eat away some bhoots, you see. Yogini: Mother,

829
00:58:19,790 --> 00:58:22,923
Marcus has made a very beautiful Indian sweets,

830
00:58:23,003 --> 00:58:24,829
but that didn’t work out.

831
00:58:24,909 --> 00:58:28,642
Shri Mataji: I don’t eat any sweets these days, you see.

832
00:58:29,409 --> 00:58:33,130
I’m going into a kind of a penance,

833
00:58:33,210 --> 00:58:36,751
for some time. No sweets for me.

834
00:58:36,831 --> 00:58:38,384
You can all have it.

835
00:58:38,464 --> 00:58:40,064
I’d like you to do that.

836
00:58:40,144 --> 00:58:43,410
A little penance is needed sometimes for me also.

837
00:58:43,490 --> 00:58:47,680
Yogini: Would you like a cup of tea, Mother?

838
00:58:47,760 --> 00:58:51,450
Shri Mataji: Yes, without milk. With lemon.

839
00:58:52,444 --> 00:58:58,330
Have you got? Yogi: Mother, I’ve got some channa upstairs.

840
00:58:58,410 --> 00:59:02,003
Shall I go and bring it for you?

841
00:59:02,083 --> 00:59:05,988
Shri Mataji:  All right, bring it, bring it.

842
00:59:06,068 --> 00:59:08,148
Channa I don’t want. [UNCLEAR:

843
00:59:08,228 --> 00:59:11,294
Little Kim?] what was happening? Where she is?

844
00:59:11,374 --> 00:59:15,160
Yogi: She just felt… she was uncomfortable, she’s…

845
00:59:15,240 --> 00:59:19,329
Shri Mataji: So just put her on something comfortable.

846
00:59:19,409 --> 00:59:23,876
Yogi: No, she’s okay, she just feels a little bit restless;

847
00:59:23,956 --> 00:59:27,818
when you’re three it’s a strain to be quiet Mother.

848
00:59:27,898 --> 00:59:32,093
Shri Mataji: Now who are the Exeter people who have come?

849
00:59:32,173 --> 00:59:35,386
Yogi: Peter and Jane, Mother. Shri Mataji: Who?

850
00:59:35,466 --> 00:59:37,999
Raise your hand. Yogi: Peter and Jane.

851
00:59:38,079 --> 00:59:40,292
Shri Mataji: Oh I see. Good.

852
00:59:40,372 --> 00:59:42,031
Nice to see you here.

853
00:59:42,111 --> 00:59:48,038
Yogi: Mother Peter had some trouble with his back since he got Realisation.

854
00:59:48,118 --> 00:59:51,006
Shri Mataji: Who had? Come along here.

855
00:59:51,086 --> 00:59:55,160
Will he be able to sit on this one? Can you?

856
00:59:55,240 --> 00:59:59,542
Yogi: Shri Mataji,

857
00:59:59,622 --> 01:00:05,966
why do we feel cool breeze

858
01:00:06,046 --> 01:00:11,164
like the vibrations?

859
01:00:11,244 --> 01:00:18,950
Shri Mataji: Because the All-pervading Power is felt like

860
01:00:19,030 --> 01:00:23,030
that when your Spirit is enlightened.

861
01:00:24,640 --> 01:00:28,871
It is existing everywhere but you never feel it before

862
01:00:28,951 --> 01:00:32,864
you start feeling it when your Spirit is awakened.

863
01:00:32,944 --> 01:00:37,557
Yogi: He says when You talk about warmth, you talk about love. Yogi:

864
01:00:37,637 --> 01:00:40,170
The warm feeling is a feeling of love.

865
01:00:40,250 --> 01:00:47,088
Shri Mataji: You see,

866
01:00:47,168 --> 01:00:57,690
we never say that it is nice to

867
01:00:57,770 --> 01:01:01,540
be boiling but we always say it’s nice to be cooling.

868
01:01:02,790 --> 01:01:05,010
All cancer patients give heat.

869
01:01:05,090 --> 01:01:09,632
Whenever anyone is diseased it gives heat. You see,

870
01:01:09,712 --> 01:01:16,270
another extreme could be this,

871
01:01:16,350 --> 01:01:21,655
you can say that, freezing; maybe. But we say,

872
01:01:21,735 --> 01:01:28,057
“Wash me and I shall be whiter than snow.” You never say that,

873
01:01:28,137 --> 01:01:32,670
“You, you burn me and I shall be brighter than charcoal.” (laughter)

874
01:01:32,750 --> 01:01:38,202
But you’ll be

875
01:01:38,282 --> 01:01:42,970
surprised.

876
01:01:43,050 --> 01:01:45,170
It is very, very temperate.

877
01:01:45,250 --> 01:01:48,850
I mean it’s not a thing that is freezingly (sic) cold.

878
01:01:48,930 --> 01:01:53,530
If it is freezingly cold that means Left Side – if you get very cold.

879
01:01:53,610 --> 01:01:58,570
I mean it can never be.

880
01:01:58,650 --> 01:02:02,763
Cool Breeze, actually, is never very cold, it’s not freezing.

881
01:02:02,843 --> 01:02:08,250
It could be hot with some people, could be very cool because of their problems.

882
01:02:08,330 --> 01:02:12,290
But if you are a normal person you feel a cooler sensation.

883
01:02:13,190 --> 01:02:16,231
Even here, how much ice people consume?

884
01:02:16,311 --> 01:02:21,231
Just think of that.

885
01:02:21,311 --> 01:02:28,980
“On the rocks!” (laughter) They are always ‘on the rocks’.

886
01:02:32,790 --> 01:02:36,220
The amount of ice cream they consume,

887
01:02:36,300 --> 01:02:42,400
the amount of ices they consume in this cold country is most surprising.

888
01:02:42,480 --> 01:02:50,285
Even your Prime Minister gave us to eat, rhubarb ice!

889
01:02:50,365 --> 01:02:53,990
(laughter) On an icy cold day.

890
01:03:01,050 --> 01:03:04,210
I mean you use much more cooling than we use.

891
01:03:10,330 --> 01:03:16,471
And even you suggest, like say somebody is very much in a heat and is getting angry,

892
01:03:16,551 --> 01:03:19,701
they say, “Cool down, cool down.” But if

893
01:03:19,781 --> 01:03:26,932
somebody is supposing is lethargic you don’t say, “Boil up!” You say,

894
01:03:27,012 --> 01:03:30,478
“Awake and be active,” but you never say, “Boil up!”

895
01:03:34,441 --> 01:03:37,574
It is slightly less than your body temperature.

896
01:03:41,271 --> 01:03:44,151
It’s not so very cooling as to freeze you.

897
01:03:44,868 --> 01:03:47,801
If it is hot, then something wrong with you.

898
01:03:47,881 --> 01:03:53,481
I mean the question ‘why?’ is such, that even if there was hot they would have said,

899
01:03:53,561 --> 01:03:57,781
“Why hot?” But [if] it is cool, it’s cool. There’s no ‘why?’

900
01:03:57,861 --> 01:04:03,185
about God. Good. Coming up.

901
01:04:03,265 --> 01:04:09,808
Very bad Swadishthana!

902
01:04:09,888 --> 01:04:12,154
The left one, it goes to the left.

903
01:04:12,234 --> 01:04:13,780
That’s the worst part.

904
01:04:16,330 --> 01:04:20,550
Because they don’t believe in giving us any peaceful time.

905
01:04:20,630 --> 01:04:24,540
If there is an earthquake, they’ll write it, first page.

906
01:04:24,620 --> 01:04:26,620
If there is somebody a ripper,

907
01:04:26,700 --> 01:04:31,300
you’ll find five columns of articles written on this horrible ripper.

908
01:04:31,380 --> 01:04:32,580
Is he your ideal?

909
01:04:35,610 --> 01:04:40,210
And about Sahaj Yoga they are not willing to write even one sentence!

910
01:04:41,610 --> 01:04:43,876
Now he is the ideal of the people!

911
01:04:46,567 --> 01:04:51,260
So shameful, I tell you, the whole thing is. Feel like vomiting.

912
01:04:54,300 --> 01:04:55,614
What depravity.

913
01:04:55,694 --> 01:05:00,720
(Mother is talking about a serial killer known as ‘The Yorkshire Ripper’)

914
01:05:00,800 --> 01:05:05,800
Another one I have got to show you, which some of you should try to answer.

915
01:05:05,880 --> 01:05:08,080
Where is that? Did you bring one?

916
01:05:08,160 --> 01:05:10,700
John? John Watkinson: Newspaper?

917
01:05:10,780 --> 01:05:14,230
Shri Mataji: John? I mean I can’t even discuss this.

918
01:05:14,310 --> 01:05:18,900
The brain trust should see it.

919
01:05:18,980 --> 01:05:26,849
I mean, how, where the mind of the people is going?

920
01:05:26,929 --> 01:05:32,744
Where they are attracted to? What did you bring? Oh God!

921
01:05:32,824 --> 01:05:35,594
Shri Mataji: I wanted the magazine.

922
01:05:35,674 --> 01:05:39,789
John: Oh, thought you just said The Daily Telegraph?

923
01:05:39,869 --> 01:05:43,869
Shri Mataji: News, Telegraph, the magazine is there. Sunday.

924
01:05:45,497 --> 01:05:47,543
Sunday Telegraph. All right.

925
01:05:47,623 --> 01:05:49,089
Gavin, you can get it.

926
01:05:49,169 --> 01:05:52,369
Some of you should get it. There’s something one

927
01:05:52,449 --> 01:05:59,960
should see – horrible. And they have tried to describe the prostitutes of Bombay.

928
01:06:00,040 --> 01:06:01,906
Are you finished with yours?

929
01:06:09,070 --> 01:06:10,470
In a very horrid way!

930
01:06:11,320 --> 01:06:14,253
Absolutely nude they have shown these women.

931
01:06:14,800 --> 01:06:17,360
In India pornography is not allowed.

932
01:06:18,997 --> 01:06:21,730
So this is a way of having a pornography.

933
01:06:21,810 --> 01:06:23,730
It’s very, very subtle.

934
01:06:23,810 --> 01:06:31,180
And that is a place where people just don’t go to!

935
01:06:31,260 --> 01:06:35,091
I mean that road nobody would go through.

936
01:06:35,171 --> 01:06:37,771
It’s regarded as an inauspicious place.

937
01:06:37,891 --> 01:06:42,557
If somebody has to go from there, they’ll come [home] and have a bath.

938
01:06:50,701 --> 01:06:52,981
Only the sailors go there mostly.

939
01:06:59,291 --> 01:07:02,691
But where is your attention is the point, you know.

940
01:07:06,641 --> 01:07:08,174
Very horrible pictures.

941
01:07:09,391 --> 01:07:11,871
You go to Nepal. I mean we never saw

942
01:07:11,951 --> 01:07:15,951
anything there! Till Gregoire told me that this is all here.

943
01:07:16,031 --> 01:07:19,831
I said, “Really, where is it?” He said, “On top.” I said,

944
01:07:19,911 --> 01:07:25,177
“Where?” He said, “Where this Japanese has gone up with three ladders, you see,

945
01:07:25,257 --> 01:07:27,523
hanging in the air projecting zoom

946
01:07:27,603 --> 01:07:34,850
lenses.” This is just to support their weaknesses, perhaps. Come in, come in.

947
01:07:36,290 --> 01:07:37,647
Come forward.

948
01:07:37,727 --> 01:07:43,006
You can move some of you this side, I think, there’s lot of room. On this side?

949
01:07:44,490 --> 01:07:49,156
I think you all can come, Graham and all that, you can come this side.

950
01:07:51,900 --> 01:07:55,288
And I think you can come. Phil?

951
01:07:55,368 --> 01:08:02,716
I mean, have I any place where

952
01:08:02,796 --> 01:08:08,357
I can talk to people,

953
01:08:08,437 --> 01:08:10,803
little bit in privacy.

954
01:08:10,883 --> 01:08:14,629
Yogini: Yes Mother we can tidy the girls’ room for you.

955
01:08:14,709 --> 01:08:16,975
Shri Mataji: All right. So I’ll go

956
01:08:17,055 --> 01:08:19,988
upstairs? Yogini: Is that all right for you?

957
01:08:20,068 --> 01:08:22,334
Another Yogini: You can go up now.

958
01:08:22,414 --> 01:08:26,747
Yogini: What if we were to go upstairs, would that not be easier?

959
01:08:26,827 --> 01:08:30,160
Yogini: Wouldn’t it be easier if we went upstairs?

960
01:08:30,240 --> 01:08:32,973
Shri Mataji: No, no, no. Quite all right.

961
01:08:33,053 --> 01:08:36,853
You know now I have bought a house which is five stories!

962
01:08:36,933 --> 01:08:38,991
Yogini: That was the problem, Mother.

963
01:08:39,071 --> 01:08:41,296
That was what we were all worried about.

964
01:08:41,376 --> 01:08:43,156
Shri Mataji: No, it’s all right.

965
01:08:43,236 --> 01:08:45,071
Yogini: Why don’t we go upstairs?

966
01:08:45,151 --> 01:08:47,320
Shri Mataji: No, no, no, I’m all right.

967
01:08:47,400 --> 01:08:49,458
Yogi: Linda it’s very tidy your room.

968
01:08:49,538 --> 01:08:52,565
Shri Mataji: Where has Cooly gone? Just call him here.

969
01:08:52,645 --> 01:08:55,037
Peter Pearce: He’s just busy at the moment.

970
01:08:55,117 --> 01:08:57,898
Peter Pearce: There’s someone at the door for him.

971
01:08:57,978 --> 01:08:59,424
Shri Mataji: Let him come.

972
01:08:59,504 --> 01:09:01,061
Somebody else could be busy!

973
01:09:01,141 --> 01:09:03,533
People think we can be on our own, you see.

974
01:09:03,613 --> 01:09:07,896
They start thinking like that, [that] we can start working it out on our own.

975
01:09:07,976 --> 01:09:11,035
That’s why if you write about chakras, be very careful.

976
01:09:11,115 --> 01:09:12,950
Nothing can be worked on you own.

977
01:09:13,030 --> 01:09:16,367
They think, “Oh, our relationship is with Mother, directly.”

978
01:09:16,447 --> 01:09:20,062
Yogi: No, this is for Sahaj Yogis; this is not the normal people.

979
01:09:20,142 --> 01:09:22,089
Shri Mataji: It is for Sahaj Yogis?

980
01:09:22,169 --> 01:09:26,174
Yogi: Yes, it’s the information to further your knowledge of Sahaj Yoga.

981
01:09:26,254 --> 01:09:29,670
To know a little bit more about in Sahaj. Shri Mataji: Oh no,

982
01:09:29,750 --> 01:09:33,866
then I would suggest that if it is the information for Sahaj Yogis – first

983
01:09:33,946 --> 01:09:37,283
thing one should say is that, what information they need is,

984
01:09:37,363 --> 01:09:39,476
that they cannot work it on their own.

985
01:09:39,556 --> 01:09:42,003
Mother only loves those who love each other.

986
01:09:42,083 --> 01:09:45,083
Anybody who thinks, “I can work it on my own,

987
01:09:45,163 --> 01:09:50,496
I have a special relationship with Mother,” should know that they are going out.

988
01:09:50,576 --> 01:09:52,442
This sentence you put first.

989
01:09:52,522 --> 01:09:55,033
Then I don’t mind writing an introduction.

990
01:09:55,113 --> 01:09:56,336
Yogi: An introduction?

991
01:09:56,416 --> 01:09:58,149
Shri Mataji: Introduction.

992
01:09:58,229 --> 01:09:59,695
Yogi: Ah, yes that’s –

993
01:09:59,775 --> 01:10:05,175
Shri Mataji: Because they will know all about chakras, and still not be in there.

994
01:10:05,255 --> 01:10:07,401
Yogi: Yes of course, of course.

995
01:10:07,481 --> 01:10:09,081
Shri Mataji: Better now?

996
01:10:09,161 --> 01:10:12,827
Shri Mataji: It is said that, “Eka hi akshara prema ka,

997
01:10:12,907 --> 01:10:15,173
Wada is ho pandita hua.” Ak-shara.

998
01:10:15,253 --> 01:10:18,653
‘Akshara’ means, actually ‘word’ in the normal way.

999
01:10:18,733 --> 01:10:20,146
But what is akshara?

1000
01:10:20,226 --> 01:10:25,925
I mean the one that is never destroyed,

1001
01:10:26,005 --> 01:10:27,650
which never diminishes.

1002
01:10:27,730 --> 01:10:35,250
So ‘ek’ – only one – word of love, the one who can read that

1003
01:10:35,330 --> 01:10:39,830
word – becomes the pandita, the one who becomes the vidvana.

1004
01:10:39,910 --> 01:10:42,845
All the rest of knowledge is useless.

1005
01:10:42,925 --> 01:10:47,210
If you can only love people who are related to you be

1006
01:10:47,290 --> 01:10:51,580
material life and not the others then that’s wrong.

1007
01:10:53,820 --> 01:10:56,381
Sahaj Yogis are your real relations.

1008
01:10:56,461 --> 01:11:01,987
You are better now.

1009
01:11:02,067 --> 01:11:03,834
Why to produce children?

1010
01:11:03,914 --> 01:11:09,047
That’s why I said that, “Don’t look after other’s children,” because all your

1011
01:11:09,127 --> 01:11:14,660
desire to be parents will be finished with that and you’ll have an excuse, you see!

1012
01:11:14,740 --> 01:11:20,910
You better get selfish on that point and produce children, for heaven’s sake.

1013
01:11:20,990 --> 01:11:24,856
All [your] marriages have turned out to be wastage for me.

1014
01:11:28,640 --> 01:11:34,175
With understanding, otherwise you will get thugs as your children.

1015
01:11:34,255 --> 01:11:37,921
With understanding, with love, with aspiration that the

1016
01:11:38,001 --> 01:11:44,680
blessings of God has to come, otherwise what [useless] marriages? Oh God.

1017
01:11:56,200 --> 01:12:00,290
As it is your foundations are weak and such great people want

1018
01:12:00,370 --> 01:12:05,965
to get their birth on this Earth and you are so adamant. Poor things.

1019
01:12:06,045 --> 01:12:11,560
Yogi: Mother? There is also Patrick from Birmingham, is a newcomer.

1020
01:12:11,640 --> 01:12:13,680
Shri Mataji: I could see that.

1021
01:12:13,760 --> 01:12:18,490
Well he’ll be all right, he’s a seeker. He’s all right.

1022
01:12:18,570 --> 01:12:20,570
You got the cool breeze?

1023
01:12:22,670 --> 01:12:25,336
Are you feeling the cool breeze Patrick?

1024
01:12:26,760 --> 01:12:30,720
Not yet? Vishuddhi he has.

1025
01:12:30,800 --> 01:12:35,830
Anybody cures his Vishuddhi, he’ll be all right. Just put your hand.

1026
01:12:36,340 --> 01:12:38,606
Douglas [Fry] will you please try.

